OL,3,CSouthport attacker's violent risk
OL,4,Cshould have been assessed in early 2020
OL,6,FThe Southport attacker should have
OL,7,Fbeen assessed under the Mental Health
OL,8,FAct, a public inquiry has heard.
OL,10,FThe Southport inquiry, sitting at
OL,11,FLiverpool Town Hall, was told the
OL,12,Fattacker refused to see psychiatrist
OL,13,FDr Anthony Molyneux in September 2023,
OL,14,Fstaying in his bedroom during a home
OL,15,Fvisit.
