OL,3,CSouthport attacker's violent risk
OL,4,Cshould have been assessed in early 2020
OL,6,FIndependent expert witness, Dr Tina
OL,7,FIrani, told the inquiry he was
OL,8,Fwithdrawn at that time, spending a
OL,9,Fconsiderable amount of time on his
OL,10,Fcomputer and was not looking after
OL,11,Fhimself, having reportedly not
OL,12,Fshowered for a month.
OL,14,FThe consultant child and adolescent
OL,15,Fforensic psychiatrist said this
OL,16,Falongside "his historic risks and
OL,17,Fdeterioration in his presentation"
OL,18,Fshould have prompted a Mental Health
OL,19,FAct assessment.
