OL,6,FThe assessment is a formal process
OL,7,Fused to determine whether someone
OL,8,Frequires hospital treatment.
OL,10,FShe said it was "likely" there would
OL,11,Fhave been no evidence to suggest he
OL,12,Fneeded treatment, but it would have
OL,13,Fgiven an opportunity to see AR face-to-
OL,14,Fface and assess his risk.
