OL,3,CSouthport attacker's violent risk
OL,4,Cshould have been assessed in early 2020
OL,6,FHe was discharged from Alder Hey Child
OL,7,Fand Adolescent Mental Health Service
OL,8,F(CAMHS) on July 23 2024, six days
OL,9,Fbefore he murdered three girls and
OL,10,Fattempted to kill 10 others when he
OL,11,Fwent to the Taylor Swift-themed
OL,12,Fworkshop armed with a knife.
OL,14,FDr Irani also said a comprehensive
OL,15,Fassessment of his violent risk should
OL,16,Fhave been undertaken in early 2020,
OL,17,Fafter he was referred to the forensic
OL,18,Fchild and adolescent mental health
OL,19,Fservice following an attack with a
OL,20,Fhockey stick on a pupil at his former
OL,21,Fschool.
