OL,3,CSouthport attacker's violent risk
OL,4,Cshould have been assessed in early 2020
OL,6,FShe said mental health services were
OL,7,Fnot adequate, focusing too much on the
OL,8,Frisks to the future attacker, and not
OL,9,Fenough on the risks he posed to others.
OL,11,FDr Irani also said a decision by
OL,12,Fpolice not to take action when they
OL,13,Ffound AR carrying a knife on a bus in
OL,14,FMarch 2022 due to his "severe autism"
OL,15,Fappeared to have been made without
OL,16,Fconsultation with a clinician.
