OL,3,CSouthport attacker's violent risk
OL,4,Cshould have been assessed in early 2020
OL,6,FShe told the inquiry his autism would
OL,7,Fnot have meant he lacked
OL,8,Fresponsibility for his actions in
OL,9,Fcarrying a knife or prevented him from
OL,10,Fgoing through the criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FThe independent expert said AR met the
OL,14,Fcriteria for a diagnosis of conduct-
OL,15,Fdissocial disorder and she thought he
OL,16,Fcould have been diagnosed "early on".
