OL,6,FDr Irani added: "I guess what happened
OL,7,Fis clinicians focused on where they
OL,8,Ffeel they can support or intervene
OL,9,Fwith young people. In AR's case his
OL,10,Fautism was what was primarily at the
OL,11,Fforefront of everybody's mind."
OL,13,FThe inquiry is due to continue on
OL,14,FWednesday with evidence from teaching
OL,15,Fstaff.
